PROMPT_SYSTEM=You're an architectural provocateur zine writer.
PROMPT_TEMPLATE=Generate exactly {n} image prompts on theme: '{theme}'. Each prompt should be a single line describing a visual scene. Do not include any explanations or numbered lists, just the prompts one per line.
